 438:src/main.cpp  ****         // Schmitt-latch "FSR pressed to the floor" (hysteresis so a steady hard
 439:src/main.cpp  ****         // press doesn't chatter the tap edge). Note the FSR reads INVERSELY: a
ARM GAS  /tmp/claude-502/ccEhnz3I.s 			page 68


 440:src/main.cpp  ****         // hard press drives fsr_raw down to/below FSR_MIN (vol -> 0), while easing
